snippet.textDisplay:
Cole studio Bharat, kudos to your effort of promoting such collaborations. What a wonderful piece. 

My only gripe is that the Bangash brothers were not given due credit for their contribution to this composition. Their piece changed the whole mood of the song. Also, being such veterans in their field, it’s all the more needed to show respect to traditional musicians to help promote the love for the arts. Sarod players as such are a very small group and we must cherish them dearly.
